attributes.long-description:
The Star Wars® saga continues in Star Wars®: The Force Unleashed™, which casts players as Darth Vader's 'Secret Apprentice' and promises to unveil new revelations about the Star Wars® galaxy. The expansive story is set during the largely unexplored era between Star Wars®: Episode III Revenge of the Sith and Star Wars®: Episode IV A New Hope. Players will assist the iconic villain in his quest to rid the universe of Jedi and face decisions that could change the course of their destiny.

A minimum 1.3GB of disk space is required.
